experiment #1 
12/29/2025 

hypothesis: 
a. if users can see their aggregated quotes, snippets, learnings, they would compile them. 
b. users want to aggregate their interesting quotes, snippets, learnings so that they can share and look back. 

user journey: 
1. user sees something interesting 
2. user texts at (617) 682-9816
3. after a week, user sees aggregated, personalized wall of snippets they've compiled 
4. user also sees recommended content 

behind the scenes journey: 
A. compile text, images, website from text msg 
B. manually update wall 
C. manually send out text on weekly basis 
D. do some sort of tagging system 

m0 requirements: 
a. Pinterest-esque wall with log in ability 
b. Ability to manually add to wall 
c. Blocks of text or images 
d. Some sort of summary 

m1 ideas: 
a. different projects
